---
layout: layout.njk
permalink: /team/
title: "Team | austroPott – Theater im Dortmunder U"
desc: "Das austroPott-Ensemble: Monika Bujinski, Michael Kamp, Harald Schwaiger und Gitta Kessler. Seit 2012 Theater mit Tiefgang im Dortmunder U."
active: team
---
    <div class="wrap page-head">
      <h1>{{ seiten.team.ueberschrift }}</h1>
      <p class="lead">{{ team.intro }}</p>
    </div>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        {%- for person in team.mitglieder %}
        <div class="person reveal">
          <figure class="person-foto frame">
            <img src="{{ person.bild | url }}" alt="Porträt von {{ person.name }}" loading="lazy">
          </figure>
          <div>
            <h3>{{ person.name }}</h3>
            {{ person.text | md | safe }}
            {%- if person.website %}
            <p><a href="{{ person.website }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ person.website | replace("https://", "") }}</a></p>
            {%- endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>
